"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented coverage-focused test for `com.diffplug.common.base.internal.Finalizer`.\n\nChanges:\n- Added `FinalizerTest.java` under:\n  - `tests/src/com.diffplug.durian/durian-core/1.2.0/src/test/java/com_diffplug_durian/durian_core/FinalizerTest.java`\n- The test starts `Finalizer` through its public `startFinalizer` API, enqueues a custom `FinalizableReference`, and verifies `finalizeReferent()` is invoked.\n- This exercises the remaining dynamic-access paths:\n  - `Finalizer.startFinalizer(...)`\n  - `Finalizer.getFinalizeReferentMethod(...)`\n  - `Finalizer.cleanUp(...)`\n- Made existing `Durian_coreTest` top-level class `public` to satisfy test class visibility requirements.\n\nPer instruction, I did not compile or run tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_01df897cf78f724f0169f7048f76f881a1b4d1949e935f88ca\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 400, "output": 701, "cacheRead": 26624, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 27725, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777796226755, "responseId": "resp_01df897cf78f724f0169f70483340c81a180ee4b512177ce9d"}, "toolResults": []}
